entry.tran: (一系列事物中)第 n 次的，第 n 位的
entry.def: If you refer to the most recent item in a series of things as the nth item, you are emphasizing the number of times something has happened.

example.ex: The story was raised with me for the nth time two days before the article appeared.
example.tran: 在我第n次被问及这件事情的两天后，相关文章登了出来。

entry.def: If something is done to the nth degree, it is done to an extreme degree.

example.ex: Ned and I discussed everything to the nth degree...
example.tran: 我和内德极为深入地讨论了每一件事。

example.ex: You're a risk-taker to the nth degree.
